<div class="about-page">
  <div class="about-card">
    <h1>About OpenLab</h1>
    <p class="about-desc">OpenLab is a computer laboratory seat reservation system built for De La Salle University. It allows students to check real-time seat availability across various lab rooms, reserve slots up to seven days in advance, and manage their bookings from any device.</p>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time lab seat availability across multiple buildings</li>
        <li>Seat reservation with 30-minute time slots</li>
        <li>Anonymous reservation option</li>
        <li>Walk-in management for lab technicians</li>
        <li>User profile management and search</li>
        <li>Reservation history and management</li>
        <li>Role-based access (Student &amp; Technician)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

